<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id79a209d0-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s2706"><num value="2706">§ 2706.</num><heading> New impoundments</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Nothing in this chapter authorizes (1) the loan of funds for construction of any new dam or other impoundment, or (2) the simple and expeditious licensing of any such new dam or other impoundment.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id79a209d1-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/95/617/tIV/s406">Pub. L. 95–617, title IV, § 406</ref>, <date date="1978-11-09">Nov. 9, 1978</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/92/3156">92 Stat. 3156</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
